    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This beauty is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you'd think she just rolled off the lot yesterday. I've been super meticulous with the upkeep, so it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
