    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero imperfections, swirl marks, or rock chips, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creases or wear, while the dashboard and trim pieces are flawless. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and documented service history from authorized dealerships. It drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that requires absolutely nothing but a new garage to call home.",
      "price": 47500.0,
