      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically, this chassis is flawless: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is documented. The suspension retains its factory-spec McPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits original paint depth with no swirl marks, and the interior is devoid of typical bolster wear. A turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
